DESCRIPTION OF YOUR CLASS DESIGN AND ALGORITHMS AND DATA STRUCTURES USED: (see assgt description for more about this)
Core Data Structures


AnagramDictionary: HashMap mapping sorted letters to lists of valid anagrams
ScoreTable: HashMap for letter-to-score lookups
Rack: Tracks available letters and their frequencies


Key Algorithms


Dictionary Building: Processes words into canonical forms
Finding Valid Words:
    Generates all possible letter combinations recursively
    Validates against dictionary
    Scores and sorts results


Process Flow


Load dictionary → Generate combinations → Validate words → Score → Sort → Display


